{
  "stem": "14552.3",
  "chunk_idx": 6,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 7.5,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And if some of them are killed on the way, no problem, there's more of them.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And then we were put into the cattle cars with one bucket on each end, and no water, and no supply, no food supply.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Mother and Jen.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And we had this-- then we were-- went on this journey.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And we-- as we went by, we were on sidings at night.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And I looked over and I saw houses where people were sitting in houses from this mountainside.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "We were on the side, and there was the valley and there was a house.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And I saw the houses and-- and the-- the smoky-- the--",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "--windows were foggy, or whatever it was.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And I was looking at them.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Do they know what they have?",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Do they understand what-- what luxury they have to be in that home, to have something to eat?",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And-- and my mind was just racing with these feelings.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And then after-- we have-- on the way there, we were-- there were other wagons coming with people from the labor camps.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And now we asked them, do you know this?",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Do you know my brother?",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Do you know this?",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And everybody was shouting questions to them.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And they said, yeah, I saw him, or yes, he died, or I don't know.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And it was going back and forth until they came around and they started to say, don't-- don't ask.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Don't do-- don't put your hands out, because they would whip.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And no water and no food was given.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And that went on, this unbelievable state.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And we were-- I think, we were about 100 people.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "In that car.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "At least 100 people.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, we were sitting.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Not laying down, but just sitting down.",
      "word_count": 7
    }
  ],
